ActCanadian Environmental Protection Act, 1999
SubjectOrder Adding Toxic Substances to Schedule 1 to the Canadian Environmental Protection Act, 1999
PrecisOrder ADDING TOXIC SUBSTANCES TO SCHEDULE 1 TO THE CANADIAN ENVIRONMENTAL PROTECTION ACT, 1999 - which adds Thiourea, 1,3-Butadiene, 2-methyl-, Oxirane, (chloromethyl)-, Colour Index Pigment Yellow 34, Colour Index Pigment Red 104, Cyclotetrasiloxane, octamethyl-, and Phenol, 2,4,6-tris(1,1-dimethylethyl)- to Schedule 1 to the Act.
